title: Breaking barriers with the b-girls and b-boys of the Youth Olympic Games
description:
We went behind-the-scenes at the first ever Youth Olympic breaking individual finals. We spoke to Bumblebee, Shigekix, and Emma after they won their medals. Don’t forget the team event will be streamed on OlympicChannel.com today.

Plus, we have all the usual headlines and tips on who to watch.
